What is Generative AI?
It uses advanced models (like large language models and generative networks) to:

Generate human-like text
Create realistic images and videos
Compose music
Write code

How it Works
Train on large datasets
Learn patterns and relationships
Generate new, similar content based on input

Key Use Cases of Generative AI
1. 📝 Content Creation
Blog writing, articles, social media posts
Marketing copy generation
Email drafting
2. 🎨 Image & Design Generation
Create artwork, logos, posters
Product design concepts
AI-generated illustrations
3. 💻 Code Generation
Auto-generate code snippets
Debugging and suggestions
Example: GitHub Copilot
4. 🎧 Audio & Voice Generation
Text-to-speech systems
AI voice assistants
Music composition
5. 🎬 Video Creation
AI-generated videos
Animation and editing
Deepfake technology (with ethical concerns)
6. 🏥 Healthcare
Drug discovery
Medical image analysis
Generating synthetic patient data
7. 🛍️ E-commerce
Personalized product recommendations
AI-generated product descriptions
Virtual try-ons
8. 🎮 Gaming
Create characters, environments, storylines dynamically
